column1: * 1906 - Actor and comedian Brother Theodore is born.
* 1918 - World War I comes to an end in a cease-fire.
* 1919 - The The Ruined Enchanter: A Fairy Ballad to J.R.R. Tolkien.
* 1956 - J.R.R. Tolkien writes Letter to Mr Britten (11 November 1956).
* 1964 - J.R.R. Tolkien writes Letter to Clyde S. Kilby (11 November 1964).
* 1993 - Poems by J.R.R. Tolkien: Volume I-III is published.
* 2011 - The Lord of the Rings: War in the North is released in Spain.
